trans-unit.source: Encapsulates a File Transfer Protocol (FTP) server's response to a request.
trans-unit.target: Innkapsler en (FTP File Transfer Protocol)-server svar på en forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: Instances of FtpWebResponse are obtained by calling the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Forekomster av FtpWebResponse hentes ved å kalle den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: The returned object must be cast to an FtpWebResponse.
trans-unit.target: Det returnerte objektet må endres til en FtpWebResponse.

trans-unit.source: When your application no longer needs the FtpWebResponse object, call the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A> method to free the resources held by the FtpWebResponse.
trans-unit.target: Når programmet trenger ikke lenger FtpWebResponse-objekt, kaller den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A>metode for å frigjøre ressurser holdes av FtpWebResponse.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A> property contains the status code returned by the server, and the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusDescription%2A> property returns the status code and a message that describes the status.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A>egenskapen inneholder statuskoden returnert av serveren, og <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusDescription%2A>egenskapen returnerer statuskoden og en melding som beskriver statusen.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusDescription%2A> </xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A>

trans-unit.source: The values returned by these properties change as the messages are returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: Verdiene som returneres av disse egenskapene endre meldingene returneres av serveren.

trans-unit.source: Any data returned by the request, such as the list of file names returned for a <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory> request, is available in the stream returned by the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.GetResponseStream%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Alle data som returneres av forespørselen, slik som listen over filnavn returnert for en <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory>ber om, er tilgjengelig i dataflyten ble returnert av den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.GetResponseStream%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.GetResponseStream%2A> </xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory>

trans-unit.source: The length of the stream data can be obtained from the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.ContentLength%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Lengden på datastrømmen kan hentes fra det <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.ContentLength%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.ContentLength%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the message sent by the FTP server when a connection is established prior to logon.
trans-unit.target: Henter meldingen som er sendt av FTP-serveren når en tilkobling er opprettet tidligere pålogging.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the banner message sent by the server; otherwise, <xref:System.String> if no message is sent.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder den banner meldingen av serveren; ellers <xref:System.String>Hvis ingen meldingen sendes.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Frees the resources held by the response.
trans-unit.target: Frigjør ressurser holdes av svaret.

trans-unit.source: The Close method closes the data stream returned by the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.GetResponseStream%2A> method if the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A> property is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Close lukker dataflyten ble returnert av den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.GetResponseStream%2A>metoden hvis den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A>egenskapen `false`.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A> </xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.GetResponseStream%2A>

trans-unit.source: During the close, data might be sent to the server on the control connection.
trans-unit.target: Under avslutning, kan data sendes til serveren for kontroll-tilkoblingen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This member outputs trace information when you enable network tracing in your application.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Dette medlemmet genererer sporingsinformasjon når du aktiverer sporing for nettverk i programmet.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Network Tracing in the .NET Framework](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [nettverk sporing i .NET Framework](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets the length of the data received from the FTP server.
trans-unit.target: Henter lengden på dataene som er mottatt fra FTP-serveren.

trans-unit.source: When a response stream is returned by the FTP server, the ContentLength property contains the number of bytes in the stream.
trans-unit.target: Når et svar-dataflyten er returnert av FTP-serveren, inneholder egenskapen ContentLength antall byte i dataflyten.

trans-unit.source: ContentLength returns −1 if no data was returned in the response or if the server did not send content length information.
trans-unit.target: ContentLength returnerer −1 Hvis ingen data ble returnert i svaret eller serveren ikke sendte innholdslengden informasjon.

trans-unit.source: The return value is greater than or equal to zero if data was or should have been returned.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som returneres er større enn eller lik null hvis data som ble eller skal returneres.

trans-unit.source: For example, for requests that use the <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory> field, the ContentLength property always returns −1.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel for forespørsler som bruker den <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory>felt, må egenskapen ContentLength returnerer alltid −1.</xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory>

trans-unit.source: For requests that use the <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.UploadFile> method, the ContentLength property is always zero.
trans-unit.target: For forespørsler som bruker den <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.UploadFile>metoden, egenskapen ContentLength er alltid null.</xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.UploadFile>

trans-unit.source: For requests that use the <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.DownloadFile> method, the property is greater than zero if the downloaded file contained data and is zero if it was empty.
trans-unit.target: For forespørsler som bruker den <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.DownloadFile>metoden, egenskapen er større enn null hvis den nedlastede filen inneholdt data og null hvis den er tomt.</xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.DownloadFile>

trans-unit.source: For requests that use the <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.GetFileSize> method, ContentLength returns the size of the specified file on the server.
trans-unit.target: For forespørsler som bruker den <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.GetFileSize>metoden, ContentLength returnerer størrelsen på den angitte filen på serveren.</xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.GetFileSize>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Int64> value that contains the number of bytes of data received from the FTP server.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Int64>verdi som inneholder antall byte med data som er mottatt fra FTP-serveren.</xref:System.Int64>

trans-unit.source: Gets the message sent by the server when the FTP session is ending.
trans-unit.target: Henter meldingen av serveren ved avslutning av FTP-økten.

trans-unit.source: The ExitMessage property is not available until the connection to the server is closed or reused.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ExitMessage er ikke tilgjengelig til tilkobling til serveren er lukket eller brukes på nytt.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A> property is `true`, the connection used by this request is not closed, which prevents the server from sending an exit message.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A>egenskapen `true`, tilkoblingen som brukes av denne forespørselen ikke er lukket, som hindrer at serveren sende meldingen avsluttes.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the exit message sent by the server; otherwise, <xref:System.String> if no message is sent.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder avsluttes meldingen av serveren; ellers <xref:System.String>Hvis ingen meldingen sendes.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the stream that contains response data sent from an FTP server.
trans-unit.target: Henter dataflyten som inneholder svardata som er sendt fra en FTP-server.

trans-unit.source: After reading the data, you must close the stream.
trans-unit.target: Etter at dataene, må du lukke dataflyten.

trans-unit.source: The stream is automatically closed when you close the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse> object that contains it.
trans-unit.target: Dataflyten lukkes automatisk når du lukker <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>objektet som inneholder det.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse>

trans-unit.source: An exception is thrown unless the request method is <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.DownloadFile> or <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory>.
trans-unit.target: Et unntak med mindre du mister forespørselmetoden <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.DownloadFile>eller <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory>.</xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.ListDirectory> </xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.DownloadFile>

trans-unit.source: A readable <xref:System.IO.Stream> instance that contains data returned with the response; otherwise, <xref:System.IO.Stream> if no response data was returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: En lesbar <xref:System.IO.Stream>-forekomst som inneholder data som er returnert med svaret; ellers <xref:System.IO.Stream>Hvis ingen svardata ble returnert av serveren.</xref:System.IO.Stream> </xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: The response did not return a data stream.
trans-unit.target: Svaret returnerte ikke en dataflyt.

trans-unit.source: Gets an empty <xref:System.Net.WebHeaderCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en tom <xref:System.Net.WebHeaderCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Net.WebHeaderCollection>

trans-unit.source: The Headers property is provided only for compatibility with other implementations of the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> and <xref:System.Net.WebResponse> classes.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen overskrifter finnes bare for kompatibilitet med andre implementeringer av den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>og <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>klasser.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: An empty <xref:System.Net.WebHeaderCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: En tom <xref:System.Net.WebHeaderCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Net.WebHeaderCollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the date and time that a file on an FTP server was last modified.
trans-unit.target: Henter datoen og klokkeslettet da en fil på FTP-server sist ble endret.

trans-unit.source: The LastModified property returns the data requested by the <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.GetDateTimestamp> method.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen LastModified returnerer dataene som ble forespurt av den <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.GetDateTimestamp>metoden.</xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.GetDateTimestamp>

trans-unit.source: For requests sent using any other method, LastModified returns <xref:System.DateTime.MinValue>.
trans-unit.target: For forespørsler sendt ved hjelp av andre metoder, returnerer LastModified <xref:System.DateTime.MinValue>.</xref:System.DateTime.MinValue>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> that contains the last modified date and time for a file.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>som inneholder den siste endrede datoen og klokkeslettet for en fil.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets the URI that sent the response to the request.
trans-unit.target: Henter URIEN som sendte svar til forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: Because of server- and resource-specific behaviors, such as redirection, the value returned by the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.RequestUri%2A> property is not always the same as the value returned by the ResponseUri property.
trans-unit.target: På grunn av server og ressursen spesifikke virkemåter, for eksempel omadressering, returneres verdien av det <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.RequestUri%2A>egenskapen er ikke alltid det samme som verdien som returneres av egenskapen ResponseUri.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.RequestUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: For requests that use the <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.UploadFileWithUniqueName> method, ResponseUri returns the name of the file on the server.
trans-unit.target: For forespørsler som bruker den <xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.UploadFileWithUniqueName>metoden ResponseUri returnerer navnet på filen på serveren.</xref:System.Net.WebRequestMethods.Ftp.UploadFileWithUniqueName>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Uri> instance that identifies the resource associated with this response.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Uri>-forekomst som identifiserer ressursen som er knyttet til dette svaret.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: Gets the most recent status code sent from the FTP server.
trans-unit.target: Henter den siste statuskoden sendt fra FTP-serveren.

trans-unit.source: The value returned by the StatusCode property is included in the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusDescription%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som returneres av StatusCode-egenskapen er inkludert i den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusDescription%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you are downloading data, the value of StatusCode changes as status codes are returned by the FTP server.
trans-unit.target: Når du laster ned data, returneres verdien av StatusCode endringer som statuskoder av FTP-serveren.

trans-unit.source: After you call the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A> method, StatusCode contains an intermediate status code.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>metoden, StatusCode inneholder en mellomliggende statuskode.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you call the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A> method, StatusCode contains the final status.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A>metoden, StatusCode inneholder endelig status.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Net.FtpStatusCode"></xref> value that indicates the most recent status code returned with this response.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Net.FtpStatusCode"> </xref> verdi som angir siste statuskoden returnert med dette svaret.

trans-unit.source: Gets text that describes a status code sent from the FTP server.
trans-unit.target: Henter tekst som beskriver en statuskode som er sendt fra FTP-serveren.

trans-unit.source: The text returned by the StatusDescription property includes the 3-digit <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A> property value.
trans-unit.target: Teksten som returneres av egenskapen StatusDescription inneholder 3 siffer <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A>egenskapsverdi.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A>

trans-unit.source: When downloading data, the value of StatusDescription changes as status codes are returned by the FTP server.
trans-unit.target: Når du laster ned, endrer verdien for StatusDescription som statuskoder returneres av FTP-serveren.

trans-unit.source: After you call the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A> method, StatusDescription contains an intermediate status code.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>metoden, StatusDescription inneholder en mellomliggende statuskode.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.GetResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you call the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A> method, StatusDescription contains the final status.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A>metoden, StatusDescription inneholder endelig status.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Close%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> instance that contains the status code and message returned with this response.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>-forekomsten som inneholder statuskoden og meldingen returnert i svaret.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Headers*> property is supported by the <xref href="System.Net.FtpWebResponse"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Headers*>egenskapen støttes av den <xref href="System.Net.FtpWebResponse"> </xref> forekomsten.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Headers*>

trans-unit.source: This property is always true for [!INCLUDE[net_v45](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen gjelder alltid [!INCLUDE[net_v45](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Boolean>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref:System.Boolean>.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Headers*> property is supported by the <xref href="System.Net.FtpWebResponse"></xref> instance; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Headers*>egenskapen støttes av den <xref href="System.Net.FtpWebResponse"> </xref> serverforekomsten; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.Headers*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the message sent by the FTP server when authentication is complete.
trans-unit.target: Henter meldingen som er sendt av FTP-serveren når godkjenning er fullført.

trans-unit.source: If the connection is being reused (the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A> property is set to `true`), the WelcomeMessage property returns the first welcome message received with the connection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis tilkoblingen er brukt på nytt (den <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A>er satt til `true`), egenskapen WelcomeMessage returnerer den første Velkommen mottatte meldingen med tilkoblingen.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest.KeepAlive%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the welcome message sent by the server; otherwise, <xref:System.String> if no message is sent.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder velkomstmelding som er sendt av serveren; ellers <xref:System.String>Hvis ingen meldingen sendes.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.String>
